Rating: 0
I made this dish for my dinner club, which includes 10 people. 3 of us (including me) thought it was ok but nothing great. 7 people couldn't eat more than one bite because the fish sauce was so strong. I had to throw away the plastic container I used to hold the fish sauce because I couldn't get the smell out. I will not make this again.

